=10440\">תחנון</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20900\">תהלים ו׳</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20883\">תהלים כה</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20866\">תהלים טו</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20851\">תפילה אחר תחנון</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16164\">תהלים כד</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16235\">תהלים מח</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16241\">תהלים פב</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16119\">תהלים צד</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16128\">תהלים פא</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16137\">תהלים פג</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20811\">תהלים קד (ברכי נפשׁי)‏</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20891\">עלינו</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=29393\">אל מלא רחמים</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16709\">תהלים כז</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=21390\">ברכות לרעך אחרי התפילה</a><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\n<p><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=21107\">Weekday Affirmations (based on the Amidah)</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=21089\">Havinenu</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=30340\">Another version of the Amidah</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=29416\">Intention for After the Amidah</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=10440\">Taḥanun</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20900\">Psalms 6</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20883\">Psalms 25</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20866\">Psalms 15</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=20851\">Untitled Prayer at the end of Taḥanun</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16164\">Psalm for Sunday: Psalms 24</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/?p=16235\">Psalm for Monday: Psalms 48</a><br />\n<a href=\"h